html:
My father once told me
Columbo had a glass eye
It was mystical knowledge
I wasn’t allowed to know more
After communism fell
He was trading car parts
Nysa Star Żuk Jelcz
And it all was clear
EU accessing Poland
Killed the industry
He voted pro EU
Never complained
Closed four stores
Changed his business
Flown river of vodka down his throat
Died in coma
title: Sector
